PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the FLYING DUST FIRST NATION BAND surrenders, for a term of 100 years, some 1,983 hectares of Flying Dust First Nation Indian Reserve No. 105D in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of leasing them to FDB Holding Corporation for commercial, industrial, institutional and agricultural purposes.
